agent_cpu.description: Fargate CPU units for the agent task.

agent_desired_count.description: Desired count for the Prefect agent ECS service.

agent_image.description: Container image for the Prefect agent (ECR image URI or other registry).

agent_memory.description: Fargate memory (MiB) for the agent task.

az_count.description: Number of AZs to use (2 recommended).

enable_nat_gateway.description: Whether to create NAT gateways for private subnet internet egress. If false, tasks must rely on VPC endpoints only.

prefect_api_key.description: Prefect API key (store in tfvars, not in VCS).

prefect_api_url.description: Prefect API URL. For Prefect Cloud typically https://api.prefect.cloud/api.

prefect_work_queue.description: Prefect work queue name the agent will poll.

s3_bucket_name.description: Optional fixed S3 bucket name for Prefect storage. If null, a unique name will be generated.

s3_prefix.description: S3 prefix for Prefect storage block (e.g., ecs-agent-bucket).
